145,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:33:17.000Z","msg":"屌 睇錯ptgf"},{"pid":"8a0da44c3d30dc9e2f910db3deae39c9101a68aa","tid":422823,"uid":52590,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:37:38.000Z","msg":"睇人玩pubg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799cb031d11f2cac04e3213b6f62b655c378d6e1","tid":422823,"uid":90562,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該同ow一樣好快過氣</blockquote><br />\now 玩法多好多，不過我同朋友商量緊邊個最先入坑，有一個買其他人應該會買，始終$188唔算貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb4be7a553618ddf0b5a647227ee7e629a65826","tid":422823,"uid":146604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"有朋友就玩咩都好玩 但呢隻得自己玩 好快悶"},{"pid":"a223bf2430b0b8044b4348828acf40d608a5dc28","tid":422823,"uid":27391,"like":39,"dislike":19,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"無咩深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你一開始rank低打新手 個個都低低能能連咩槍搭咩子彈都唔熟 一定易生存<br />\n<br />\n我就同fd玩開4排，gameplay勁多元化<br />\n<br />\n唔同地型唔同圈位 攻定守 走定留 點樣同步攻擊滅人條team 點根據有既資源安排戰術分工 點攻樓 點防樓 點用制高點反擊<br />\n<br />\n開咩車 點開車 繞咩路線安全 點伏擊人地架車<br />\n<br />\n每一局都係未知 隊員之間需要大量磨合 決策仲要夠快 4排係可以救返起隊友 見人就射基本上係唔work(新手rank另計）<br />\n<br />\n個種互相偵察-發現-戰術-滅隊既快感 再加上次次決戰圈係唔同地型 唔同既隊伍狀態<br />\n<br />\n居然有人會話無深度 我就玩得好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c91d6f939d91c485b488e30ce14e842420991e","tid":422823,"uid":130365,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"真係好玩WO<br />\n佢steam 個player online 超越左CSGO 同DOTA2 做榜首<br />\n我諗廢game都幾難做到咁既成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cb4ee8d169538b6a7075a05d0eae533943330b","tid":422823,"uid":38394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:34:43.000Z","msg":"玩